Package tage.rml

Class Degreef

java.lang.Object
tage.rml.Degreef
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Angle>, Angle
public final class Degreef extends Object implements Angle
An immutable single-precision floating point representation of an Angle, measured in degrees.
Author:
Raymond L. Rivera
